    overview: "The Marathon County Executive Committee approved placing County Administrator on year six of the pay scale following a closed session performance review, and ratified a local state of emergency declaration related to a recent snow emergency. The committee also received a preview of 68 rules review recommendations that will be discussed at the next meeting.",
